        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p></p><h3><strong>McGowan Sherpa Gilet (Black & Brown)</strong></h3><p>Designed for golfers who love a rugged yet cosy aesthetic, the <strong>McGowan Sherpa Gilet</strong> is available in classic black and brown. This piece is perfect for transitioning between seasons, providing warmth during chilly mornings while maintaining a lightweight feel for afternoon rounds. Whether paired with a sweater or worn as a standalone outer layer, this gilet brings both comfort and a sense of understated luxury to your game.</p><h3><strong>Harrison L/S Polo Sweater (Black & Navy)</strong></h3><p>Combining the comfort of a sweater with the sleek design of a polo, the <strong>Harrison L/S Polo Sweater</strong> offers the best of both worlds. Available in timeless black and navy colourways, this piece is perfect for golfers who want a touch of formality while maintaining the soft, luxurious feel of a sweater. Its versatility makes it an ideal choice for both on-course play and post-round socialising.</p><h3><strong>Rex Wool Jacket (Heather)</strong></h3><p>Perfect for colder weather, the <strong>Rex Wool Jacket</strong> in heather provides warmth without compromising on style. Made from premium wool, this jacket is ideal for winter golfing sessions or casual wear, offering both sophistication and comfort for golfers who value luxury in their outerwear.</p>"
          }
        }
