          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The <strong>Students Golf Collection</strong> is designed for modern golfers who prioritise both fashion and functionality. It caters particularly well to young professionals and style-conscious athletes who want to look and feel their best while performing on the course. This collection goes beyond traditional golf wear by offering pieces that seamlessly transition into casual, everyday fashion, making it ideal for those who value versatility in their wardrobe.</p><p>Whether you're a seasoned golfer looking for high-performance clothing or a casual player seeking stylish attire, the Students Golf Collection has something for everyone. Its blend of luxury fabrics, innovative designs, and attention to detail make it the perfect choice for those who want to make a statement both on and off the course.</p>"
          }
        }
