          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As the colder months approach, it's essential to be prepared with the right gear. The <strong>Students Golf Collection</strong> offers a range of winter-ready options, from beanies to wool jackets, ensuring that golfers can stay warm without sacrificing style or performance. Investing in high-quality, functional golf apparel not only enhances your game but also ensures you remain comfortable no matter the weather.</p><p>For those looking for the best golf clothing for winter, pieces like the <strong>Rex Wool Jacket</strong> and <strong>McGowan Sherpa Gilet</strong> are must-haves, providing both warmth and elegance on the course. Pair these with the <strong>Harrison L/S Polo Sweater</strong> for a polished look that keeps you comfortable from the first tee to the final hole.</p>"
          }
        }
